Indeed the truth of these stories is clear to see in thexstatues themselves, where it is shaped in bronze in the prints of their crimes. What means the figure of the attendant bird that is always attached to Jupiter? Of course it is the swift armour-bearer- pander that carried the debauched youths to the tyrant.
